Comment: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:36.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sign: I want to thank you. Please come to the gym storage room at 12. Kuronuma Sawako
Comment: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:35.70,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chilling...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.80,0:01:01.91,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:02.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:06.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:09.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you got helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:12.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try talking to him more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:17.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just the two of you, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:26.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might find something in him if you talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:31.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He helped you out, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the same as Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.65,0:01:35.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, he's the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:46.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't avoid you or anything either, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:51.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:54.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game's starting, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.59,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:05.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to see Kazehaya-kun play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:13.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he used to play baseball in middle school, and I really wanted to see him play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:19.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to know more about Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:26.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, you don't know anything about Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:31.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you feel the same way about him as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:38.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching him since middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On rainy days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:41.26,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,On rainy days?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.65,0:02:44.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Windy days too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.01,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Windy days too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in snowstorms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:47.52,KimiTodo-Overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in snowstorms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:51.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I talked to him whenever I had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:54.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I made sure he wouldn't get a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:55.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.71,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:04.16,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:08.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's how well I know Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:12.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I started to feel this way just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:13.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:15.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.74,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:30.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep your eyes off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:39.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk as if you know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:46.20,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd always be in your sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.66,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.69,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd always be thinking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.73,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,You always see his face before you fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.80,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was so new to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was special, what I was feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:08.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I really don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:15.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if I'd feel this way even if it wasn't Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:19.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or if there's anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:30.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know more about Kazehaya-kun and about my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike! Batter out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:37.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try talking to Sanada-kun properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:44.47,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She actually took the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:51.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do things my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:58.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kurumi-chan, what about the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.86,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wonder if she didn't want to watch it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:12.45,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya-kun must be really special to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:14.33,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been watching him all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out with him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Go out with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.17,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so Kurumi-chan has a crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.13,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.81,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A crush?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:42.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought of that word until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:52.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're through round one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.40,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.03,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.79,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.50,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:08.90,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell with your hair done differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tomo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:18.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go cheer for our volleyball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.75,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can come too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.24,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:27.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to go cheer for Ayane-chan and Chizu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ekko's playing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:40.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:50.07,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be alone all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:54.09,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around me is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:07:00.27,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't have been this way if even one of us was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:04.64,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for Kazehaya-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:10.61,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably wouldn't have known how nice everyone is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:15.37,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My world changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:21.06,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiration, respect, romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.77,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I feel either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:27.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:30.38,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada's the same as Kazehaya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:38.60,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll find out if I talk to Sanada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.39,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll find some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think girls' volleyball and boys' soccer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sakako—I mean, Sawako...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.30,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuranuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.69,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:18.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, like “black.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroyama's cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:29.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said yama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic ball from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:44.60,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:47.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just because I was right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:09:00.48,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel like I wish I'd caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls' soccer and boys' softball, all good for round one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free steak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.97,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check the sports day committee schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What year, what class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:19.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:24.44,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, never mind, I'll find it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:25.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:26.40,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:34.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.84,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:40.85,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.14,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.89,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:50.88,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The first afternoon block is clearing the field, and taking the equipment into the storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.94,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're done, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:57.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:59.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:07.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that crazy smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.34,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.58,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,always been watching him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for Chizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:43.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Yano Ayane-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Sawako-chan and Chizu-chan's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the same middle school as Chizu, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you using for foundation and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:07.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight it'll be a pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.56,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my sister's really expensive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:13.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were rumors about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:22.53,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People shouldn't believe that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.64,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to be an idiot to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:31.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you heard the rumor too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.87,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell it to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:33.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never believed it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just overheard a bunch of girls talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.86,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:44.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine you spreading rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:56.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was someone who liked him, who spread that rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:12:00.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Sawako was in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:04.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even worse with me and Chizu backing her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:07.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So setting aside the rumor about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:12.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of the rumors about Chizu were actually true but greatly exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:18.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figure it was someone from the same school he was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she'd do if Kazehaya found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:31.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't really doubt someone without any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:36.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been talking for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:46.95,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should go; the game's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.16,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:13:00.26,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's not easy, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's seriously upfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's playing next too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got more than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:17.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the committee too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.98,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing afterwards, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.09,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat lunch then nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:26.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:28.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.21,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,My nap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:45.19,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I'll nap outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:46.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.23,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the gym storage room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.93,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Not easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:14:00.01,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I just miscalculated a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.93,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:06.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And really red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is “red” a compliment to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what now? Lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:19.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:20.35,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:22.88,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:27.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:32.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada-kun helped me when I was about to get hit by a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.55,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.31,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryu did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:37.58,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not all bad after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:42.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's something I want to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.08,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand it myself either,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:49.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't know how to explain it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.34,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:55.29,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me out once I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.84,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confused, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:08.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't get thrown off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:14.50,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what you feel is right for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.41,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:24.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Sawako has a lot to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:25.73,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:30.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have some work to do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.45,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin looks evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:41.13,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see Sanada?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.78,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.21,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talked to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:54.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I said something bad to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.43,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.10,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada-kun was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:02.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sanada-kun went to the gym storage room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kurumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like she's a strong rival, but she's a real pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.38,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sanada-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.49,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.39,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuro—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:47.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma, Sawako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.28,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:54.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:59.46,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, why does this letter say exactly what I had in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:06.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks for saving my life earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.12,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can continue living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:14.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that ball had that much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.72,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:17.89,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.79,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.25,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:44.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:59.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, like, when you like someone not just as friends but as someone special—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.82,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you don't need to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.32,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.27,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all about Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.52,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:20.76,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd make a perfect couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.99,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.01,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.42,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.65,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.06,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:50.77,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking, Kuronuma would be like, “This is my work.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.68,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazehaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.33,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you rejected Sawako-chan before summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.15,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:08.04,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:09.83,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:17.54,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never confessed to me to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:23.05,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like she likes me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.66,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:29.48,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said “no way” when I asked her if she wanted to go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:35.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't look like she cared about you earlier anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.07,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During softball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.57,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was staring at Sanada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:49.20,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't help but fall in love with someone, if they saved you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:59.96,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cheer her on if she likes him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:03.22,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when have you liked Yoshida-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.61,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:07.11,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:08.47,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.81,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know she was special?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:22.03,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to answer logically?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.67,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always special to me by the time I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.17,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't compare her to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:38.37,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does it make her special if you can't compare her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.36,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.51,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.94,KimiTodo-Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Should it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:07.00,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, let's cheer her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:31.63,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt strongly, very strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:34.14,KimiTodo-Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Love
